Aku sering berlibur.

114
00:11:24,724 --> 00:11:27,184
- Seberapa sering?
- Belasan kali sehari.

115
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:29,145
Tempat kesukaanku.

116
00:11:30,563 --> 00:11:32,231
Kepulauan Maladewa.

117
00:11:34,567 --> 00:11:36,736
Tempat berlibur pribadiku.

118
00:11:36,861 --> 00:11:39,614
Jika situasi berat bagiku,
aku beristirahat lima menit,

119
00:11:39,739 --> 00:11:42,033
dan pergi ke sana.

120
00:11:42,116 --> 00:11:45,244
Aku memusatkan pikiran
pada kekosongan.

121
00:11:51,751 --> 00:11:54,712
- Ini. Ambillah.
-Tidak. Aku tak bisa.

122
00:11:54,795 --> 00:11:57,715
Ambillah, karena kau memerlukannya
